  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  At least 18 years of age

          -  Able to sign informed consent

          -  Vaginal laceration that requires sutures but does not involve the anal sphincter
             (third-degree tear) or rectal mucosa (fourth-degree tear)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Inability to speak and understand English or Spanish

          -  Previous diagnosis of vulvodynia, dyspareunia, or other chronic vulvar pain syndrome

          -  Extensive perineal warts or vulvar varicosities
      </textblock>
